Instruction on installing all the packages to build and run ade, strting with only standard CentOS 7 installation


Install wget and git
	sudo yum install wget git-core

Install epel repo
	wget https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
	sudo yum install epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm

Install c++, bison, flex
	sudo yum group install "Development Tools"

Install Tcl and qt3
	sudo yum install tcl-devel qt3-devel ksh itcl-devel

Install all Run-time dependent packages : required to run ade
	sudo yum install tcl tk ksh libstdc++ qt3 itcl iwidgets blt tcllib bwidget


Clone the repo
	git clone https://github.com/nefelus/Athena-OpenROAD.git

Compile and Build
	Athena-OpenROAD/zrouter/src/
	make clean
	make 
	make install

Set Binary and Lib Paths to run ade
	vi set_ade_env.bash 
		set prefix_path in RELEASE
			RELEASE=<prefix_path>/Athena-OpenROAD/zrouter
		set tcl 5 or 6 
			TCL_LIBRARY=/usr/lib64/tcl8.5
			TK_LIBRARY=/usr/lib64/tk8.5
			BLT_LIBRARY=/usr/share/tcl8.5/blt2.4

	source set_ade_env.bash 
	test location of ade with
		which ade

